WEBVTT

00:01.653 --> 00:04.221
-PREVIOUSLY ON "OUTSIDERS"...

00:04.917 --> 00:06.528
-[ LAUGHS ]
-Should I call the police?

00:06.658 --> 00:08.530
-NO, THEY'RE USELESS.
THE NEW SHERIFF'S AN OXY FREAK.

00:08.660 --> 00:10.488
-I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE.

00:10.619 --> 00:14.405
AND YOU GET SOME HELP, OR I'M
TAKING THAT BOY AWAY FROM YOU.

00:14.536 --> 00:16.016
-THE BREN'IN'S WOKE UP.

00:16.146 --> 00:18.757
-WELL, WHAT A GLORIOUS DAY.

00:18.888 --> 00:20.629
-I KNOW WHAT YOU DID.

00:20.759 --> 00:22.979
AND THE ONLY REASON
YOUR HEART IS STILL BEATIN'

00:23.110 --> 00:24.546
IS YOU'RE MY SON.

00:24.676 --> 00:26.461
DON'T EVER LEAVE ME ALONE
WITH HIM AGAIN.

00:26.591 --> 00:28.419
-BIG FOSTER IS GOING AFTER GUNS.

00:28.550 --> 00:30.943
-THIS HERE...
THIS IS THE PATH TO SALVATION.

00:31.074 --> 00:32.902
-FOR 200 YEARS,
THIS MOUNTAIN'S BEEN ENOUGH.

00:33.033 --> 00:34.643
AND BRINGING GUNS UP HERE,

00:34.773 --> 00:36.427
IT'S -- IT'S AN INSULT
TO HER POWER.

00:36.558 --> 00:37.907
[ SIREN WAILING ]

00:38.038 --> 00:40.475
CAN YOU JUST HELP ME
PROTECT HER, PLEASE?

00:42.042 --> 00:43.434
-GET OUT OF HERE!

00:43.565 --> 00:45.871
[ GUNFIRE ]

00:46.002 --> 00:47.438
-WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE OUT HERE!

00:47.569 --> 00:50.137
[ ENGINES RUMBLING ]

00:50.267 --> 00:52.661
[ SIREN WAILING ]

00:52.791 --> 00:55.185
[ LOUD CRASH ]

00:55.316 --> 00:58.754
♪♪

01:01.148 --> 01:04.064
[ DOOR WHIRRING ]

01:04.194 --> 01:06.153
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

01:06.283 --> 01:07.545
[ LID THUDS ]

01:10.374 --> 01:14.857
-[ PANTING ]

01:23.996 --> 01:27.870
♪♪

01:28.000 --> 01:31.091
[ VOMITING ]

01:47.019 --> 01:49.021
[ GRUNTS SOFTLY ]

01:54.766 --> 01:57.117
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

02:18.225 --> 02:20.270
[ KEYS JANGLE ]

02:23.186 --> 02:25.493
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

02:27.059 --> 02:28.278
[ TIRES PEAL ]

02:32.108 --> 02:34.850
[ ENGINE TURNS OFF ]

02:34.980 --> 02:36.939
[ EXHALES ]

02:45.121 --> 02:48.255
[ GRUNTS ]

02:48.385 --> 02:51.606
[ A.T.V RATTLING ]

02:51.736 --> 02:54.957
[ THUDDING ]

02:55.087 --> 02:57.264
[ VULTURES SCREECHING ]

02:57.394 --> 03:00.528
[ PANTING ]

03:02.747 --> 03:05.185
[ SCREECHING CONTINUES ]

03:05.315 --> 03:07.578
SHOO!

03:07.709 --> 03:09.493
SHOO! GET!

03:09.624 --> 03:10.886
GET OUT!

03:11.016 --> 03:12.366
[ SCREECHING CONTINUES ]

03:12.496 --> 03:14.672
GO! SHOO!

03:14.803 --> 03:18.198
SHOO!
[ PANTING ]

03:18.328 --> 03:19.851
[ SCREECHING CONTINUES ]

03:19.982 --> 03:22.550
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

03:26.554 --> 03:28.469
[ SCREECHING CONTINUES ]

03:30.688 --> 03:34.388
♪♪

03:34.518 --> 03:38.566
-♪ THE DAWN IS UP, THERE'S
FIRE ON THE MOUNTAIN ♪

03:38.696 --> 03:42.613
♪ THEY'LL HAVE TO ANSWER
FOR THEIR CROOKED PLAN ♪

03:42.744 --> 03:45.703
♪ THE HOLLOWS
WILL SURROUND THEM ♪

03:45.834 --> 03:48.053
♪ AND THEY'LL GO RUNNIN'

03:48.184 --> 03:51.448
♪ BACK TO THE WRETCHED REALM
THEY CAME ♪

03:53.668 --> 04:00.109
♪ NOR WILL THE DOGS OF HELL
REFRAIN ♪

04:00.240 --> 04:05.767
♪ AND THE LAND WILL SUFFER
THOSE WHO PAID ♪

04:12.730 --> 04:17.039
[ ENGINES RUMBLING ]

04:22.610 --> 04:25.395
[ ENGINES TURN OFF ]

04:25.526 --> 04:29.138
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

04:30.618 --> 04:32.184
-HEY, WHERE MY BOY?

04:32.315 --> 04:35.840
-WE SCATTERED.
HE'LL BE ALONG PRESENT.

04:35.971 --> 04:39.279
-WHERE'S TICE?
-OH, I'M SURE HE'S FINE.

04:43.718 --> 04:47.199
[ DOOR CREAKING ]

04:48.853 --> 04:50.725
-[ SIGHS ]

04:58.515 --> 05:00.343
[ BAG THUDS ]

05:22.452 --> 05:25.629
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

05:25.760 --> 05:28.415
[ HAMMERING ]

05:30.155 --> 05:32.897
[ CHICKEN CLUCKING ]

05:35.422 --> 05:39.382
-HOW YOU THINK THEM SUMBITCHES
KNEW TO BE WAITIN' FOR US?

05:39.513 --> 05:41.471
-I DON'T KNOW, FA.
-NO?

05:41.602 --> 05:43.386
-NO. W-WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

05:43.517 --> 05:48.130
-WELL...SOMEBODY MUST'VE
SENT WORD.

05:48.260 --> 05:50.393
-WELL, I DON'T KNOW HOW
IT GOT DOWN THERE.

05:50.524 --> 05:52.787
-YEAH.
-WENT DOWN EARLIER TODAY.

05:52.917 --> 05:56.138
OBVIOUS DIDN'T GO RIGHT.

05:56.268 --> 05:58.532
-WHEN DO THINGS EVER GO RIGHT
DOWN THERE?

05:58.662 --> 06:02.187
-RUMOR HAS IT HE TRIED TO STEAL
SOME FIRE.

06:02.318 --> 06:04.755
-UH-HUH.

06:04.886 --> 06:06.844
-PLAN COMBUSTED, SO TO SPEAK.

06:06.975 --> 06:09.238
HE DOESN'T LEARN TOO FAST,
DOES HE?

06:09.369 --> 06:10.761
-NOPE.

06:10.892 --> 06:12.589
-WHERE YOU GOIN'?

06:12.720 --> 06:14.983
YOU SHOULD BE DOWN THERE
LOOKING FOR MY BOY.

06:15.113 --> 06:17.681
-WHAT HAPPENED, SHURN?
-HEY. YOU STAY OUT OF THIS.

06:17.812 --> 06:20.205
HE'S FINE.
-I'LL TELL YOU WHAT HAPPENED.

06:20.336 --> 06:22.251
TICE WENT DOWN WITH THEM
THIS MORNIN'

06:22.382 --> 06:23.513
TO DO HISMISCHIEF.

06:23.644 --> 06:24.993
HE AIN'T COME BACK.

06:25.123 --> 06:27.169
-YEAH, WELL,

06:27.299 --> 06:30.085
MAYBE HE WANT A SPELL AWAY
FROM YOUR NAGGIN' ASS.

06:30.215 --> 06:33.218
-WHAT WERE YOU DOIN' DOWN THERE?

06:33.349 --> 06:35.177
YOU BETTER TELL ME NOW, SON.

06:35.307 --> 06:37.353
BE WORSE IF SOMEBODY ELSE
HAS TO.

06:37.484 --> 06:39.529
-IT'S MY DUTY TO PROTECT US.

06:39.660 --> 06:43.403
-YOU THEFTED SOME MORE GUNS.
AM I RIGHT?

06:44.752 --> 06:46.406
SO LET'S SEE 'EM.

06:46.536 --> 06:48.930
-WELL, WE WENT AFTER THEM,
BUT WE CHANGED OUR MIND.

06:49.060 --> 06:50.714
-YOU'RE NOT WISE ENOUGH
FOR THAT.

06:50.845 --> 06:53.064
-YES, MA'AM. YOU MAY BE RIGHT.

06:53.195 --> 06:56.590
-AND IF ALL YOU DID DOWN THERE
WAS CHANGE YOUR MIND,

06:56.720 --> 06:58.592
WHERE'S HER BOY?

06:58.722 --> 07:01.333
-UH, WELL, UH, TICE, HE NEVER
GONE ON A RUN BEFORE.

07:01.464 --> 07:03.684
MAYBE...I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE HE'S LOST.

07:03.814 --> 07:06.600
OR MAYBE HE WENT TO SEE
A MOVIE. HUH?

07:06.730 --> 07:08.906
[ LAUGHTER ]

07:09.037 --> 07:10.430
-[ SIGHS ]
[ Under breath ] DAMN IT.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.910
[ Normal voice ] HE AIN'T LOST.

07:15.783 --> 07:17.872
I SEEN HIM.

07:19.613 --> 07:22.790
THE LAW WAS ALL AROUND.
RED LIGHTS.

07:22.920 --> 07:25.880
THEY PUT HIM IN A BAG.
THEY -- THEY TOOK HIM AWAY.

07:26.010 --> 07:28.273
TICE... [ INHALES DEEPLY ]

07:28.404 --> 07:30.798
HE AIN'T LOST.
HE'S -- HE'S DEAD.

07:30.928 --> 07:33.235
-[ Voice breaking ] NO.

07:33.365 --> 07:34.497
NO!

07:34.628 --> 07:38.196
[ SCREAMING ]

07:39.546 --> 07:41.286
-WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!
-LET ME GO!

07:41.417 --> 07:42.505
-SHURN, JUST --
-LET ME GO!

07:42.636 --> 07:44.115
-SHURN --
-I'M-A CUT YOU!

07:44.246 --> 07:45.639
-SHURN, SHURN, SHURN,
LOOK AT ME. LOOK AT ME.

07:45.769 --> 07:48.076
-LOOK, I-I PROTECTED HIM. OKAY?

07:48.206 --> 07:49.773
I PROTECTED HIM.
-[ SOBBING ]

07:49.904 --> 07:51.819
-AND THEY SET ON US,
THEY FIRED AT US, LIKE AN ARMY!

07:51.949 --> 07:53.864
OKAY, I SAVED HIM.

07:53.995 --> 07:55.910
NOW HE WAS WITH US WELL AND GOOD
WHEN WE LEFT.

07:56.040 --> 07:58.390
-[ CONTINUES SOBBING ]
-IF SOMETHING HAPPENED TO HIM,

07:58.521 --> 08:00.001
IT WAS ON ACCOUNT
OF HIS OWN DOIN'.

08:00.131 --> 08:03.352
-EVERYTHING YOU DO
JUST DIGS US DEEPER.

08:03.483 --> 08:06.442
HOW'S THAT BOY SUPPOSED
TO BE BURIED UP HERE NOW?

08:06.573 --> 08:08.705
-WELL, I'LL GO BACK DOWN THERE
AND I'LL FETCH HIS BODY.

08:08.836 --> 08:11.578
-ONLY PLACE YOU'RE GOIN'
IS TO CHAINS.

08:11.708 --> 08:13.057
FETCH THE CHAINS!

08:13.188 --> 08:14.798
-NOW LOOK, COME ON!
YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

08:14.929 --> 08:17.453
-NOW YOU GOING WILLINGLY OR NOT?

08:17.584 --> 08:19.150
-WELL, I CAN'T
BRING THE BOY BACK UP

08:19.281 --> 08:21.544
IF I'M UP HERE, CAN I?
-TOO LATE.

08:21.675 --> 08:23.851
THEY ALREADY TOOK HIS BODY.

08:23.981 --> 08:26.375
NOW ARE YOU GOING
TO YOUR PUNISHMENT,

08:26.506 --> 08:29.683
OR DO I HAVE TO ORDER THESE BOYS
TO TAKE YA?

08:29.813 --> 08:33.382
-WELL, I AM SORRY. I AM SORRY
THAT THE BOY GOT HURT.

08:33.513 --> 08:36.254
BUT YOU GOT NO IDEA
THE THREAT THAT THEY POSE!

08:36.385 --> 08:38.126
YOU AIN'T BEEN DOWN THERE
IN 40 YEARS!

08:38.256 --> 08:40.041
-TAKE HIM AWAY!
-NO, NO, NO, NO.

08:40.171 --> 08:41.564
OKAY, WAIT A MINUTE.
LISTEN TO ME. LISTEN TO ME!

08:41.695 --> 08:43.348
ALL OF YOU, LISTEN TO ME!

08:43.479 --> 08:46.526
'CAUSE WE FOLLOW HER
TO OUR GRAVES!

08:46.656 --> 08:48.310
ALL RIGHT? TO OUR GRAVES!

08:48.440 --> 08:50.747
-TAKE HIM TO THE BOX!
DO IT NOW!

08:50.878 --> 08:52.009
-HEY! HEY! BACK OFF!
-DO IT NOW!

08:52.140 --> 08:53.358
-YOU BACK OFF!

08:53.489 --> 08:54.621
-DON'T MAKE IT WORSE
ON YOURSELF.

08:54.751 --> 08:56.144
-YOU'RE TURNING AGAINST ME, TOO?

08:56.274 --> 08:57.754
-DON'T MAKE IT WORSE --
-YOU'RE TURNING --

08:57.885 --> 09:00.540
HEY! HEY! HEY! HEY!

09:00.670 --> 09:02.454
[ GRUNTING ]

09:02.585 --> 09:04.413
[ CHAINS RATTLING ]
-[ CONTINUES GRUNTING ]

09:04.544 --> 09:05.849
[ SHACKLES CLICKING ]

09:05.980 --> 09:08.939
[ GRUNTING CONTINUES ]

09:18.558 --> 09:20.951
-WHAT DID YOU DO?

09:23.214 --> 09:25.608
-COME ON. LIKE YOU DON'T KNOW.

09:25.739 --> 09:29.569
I DID WHAT YOU ASKED ME TO DO --
STOP 'EM.

09:29.699 --> 09:32.397
YOU SHOULD BE THANKIN' ME.

09:32.528 --> 09:35.705
-BHRADAIN AND ENOCH TOLD SHURN
THEY WERE SET UP.

09:37.228 --> 09:39.840
-I MADE ONE CALL
TO THE GUN SHOP, G'WIN.

09:39.970 --> 09:43.278
ONE PHONE CALL, THAT'S IT.

09:43.408 --> 09:45.585
-DID YOU WANT PEOPLE
TO GET HURT?

09:45.715 --> 09:47.978
-NO, I DID WHAT
YOU ASKED ME TO DO.

09:48.109 --> 09:50.633
DOES FOSTER HAVE GUNS? DOES HE?

09:50.764 --> 09:53.418
-TICE IS DEAD.

09:54.855 --> 09:57.597
-[ Whispers ] I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

09:57.727 --> 09:59.860
[ Normal voice ] OKAY,
MAYBE I THOUGHT BIG FOSTER

09:59.990 --> 10:01.513
WOULD BE THE ONE THAT ENDED UP
GETTING KILLED.

10:01.644 --> 10:05.082
I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW.
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

10:05.213 --> 10:09.913
AW, SHIT! I DON'T KNOW.
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

10:17.747 --> 10:19.140
-WHERE YOU GOIN'?

10:19.270 --> 10:21.577
-IF THE LAW FOUND THE BODY
LIKE HASIL SAID,

10:21.708 --> 10:24.058
IT MEANS THE POLICE ARE
KEEPING HIM IN THE MORGUE.

10:24.188 --> 10:26.756
IT'S A PLACE WHERE THE POLICE
KEEP UNCLAIMED BODIES.

10:26.887 --> 10:30.934
-Y-YOU'RE -- YOU'RE GONNA TALK
TO THE POLICE?

10:31.065 --> 10:33.720
-HE NEEDS TO BE BURIED
ON THE MOUNTAIN, G'WIN.

10:33.850 --> 10:35.635
IF I DON'T BRING HIS BODY BACK,

10:35.765 --> 10:37.637
HIS SPIRIT WILL HUNT ME DOWN
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE,

10:37.767 --> 10:39.203
AND I CAN'T HAVE THAT.

10:40.596 --> 10:42.859
-HUNT USDOWN.

10:45.427 --> 10:47.647
BOTH OF US.

10:52.477 --> 10:53.870
[ EXHALES ]

11:03.097 --> 11:05.708
[ MAN ON TV
SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

11:07.841 --> 11:10.321
[ DOOR CREAKING ]
-WADE?

11:14.674 --> 11:15.892
WADE.

11:16.023 --> 11:18.721
-[ SNORING ]

11:18.852 --> 11:19.983
-WADE.

11:20.114 --> 11:21.593
-[ INHALES SHARPLY ] HUH?

11:21.724 --> 11:22.943
-BACK DOOR WAS UNLOCKED.

11:23.073 --> 11:26.686
I'VE BEEN CALLING ALL DAY.

11:26.816 --> 11:31.560
-I THINK I, UH, I MUST'VE HAD
MY RINGER OFF.

11:31.691 --> 11:34.432
-YOU OKAY?
-[ INHALES DEEPLY ] YEAH.

11:34.563 --> 11:37.784
[ GRUNTS ] YEAH. I THINK
I'M COMING DOWN WITH SOMETHIN'.

11:37.914 --> 11:39.437
-UM... [ CLEARS THROAT ]

11:39.568 --> 11:41.265
WE'RE LOOKING INTO A HIT-AND-RUN
OFF KATZ ROAD.

11:41.396 --> 11:43.790
WE'RE THINKING IT MIGHT
BE ONE OF THEM FARRELLS.

11:43.920 --> 11:46.793
-[ GRUNTS ] ONE OF THEM, UH,
HIT SOMEBODY?

11:46.923 --> 11:49.883
-N-NO. UH, ONE OF THEMGOT HIT.

11:50.013 --> 11:52.537
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

11:52.668 --> 11:54.104
[ CHAINS RATTLING ]

11:57.107 --> 11:58.805
[ FOLIAGE RUSTLING ]

11:58.935 --> 12:01.546
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

12:04.549 --> 12:06.551
-I DESERVE TO BE HERE.

12:06.682 --> 12:09.032
I...I KNOW THAT NOW.

12:09.163 --> 12:11.600
I WAS ONLY TRYING TO DO RIGHT
BY US.

12:11.731 --> 12:15.125
I LEARNED MY LESSON.

12:15.256 --> 12:16.736
YOU GOTTA BELIEVE ME.

12:16.866 --> 12:18.738
-YOU DON'T GET TO TELL ME
WHAT I GOTTA BELIEVE,

12:18.868 --> 12:20.783
YOU WASTE OF FLESH.

12:20.914 --> 12:23.655
THE ONLY THING I'M OBLIGED TO DO

12:23.786 --> 12:26.963
IS MAKE SURE YOU DO NO MORE HARM
TO THIS FAMILY.

12:29.792 --> 12:32.403
YOU DIDN'T KNOW I HAD THIS,
DID YOU?

12:32.534 --> 12:35.885
I HAD TO PROTECT MYSELF
AGAINST YOUR FA, DIDN'T I?

12:36.016 --> 12:38.975
HE DIED BY HIS FIRE,
AND SO WILL YOU.

12:39.106 --> 12:42.849
-ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.
YOU'RE RIGHT, MA.

12:42.979 --> 12:46.940
ALL RIGHT, I DESERVE TO PERISH.
I DO. ALL RIGHT?

12:47.070 --> 12:50.030
BUT JUST LET ME TRY
AND MAKE THINGS RIGHT.

12:50.160 --> 12:52.293
YOU CALL A CIRCLE. ALL RIGHT?

12:52.423 --> 12:56.384
AND LET THEM PUNISH ME
THE WAY THEY SEE FIT.

12:56.514 --> 13:01.606
-OHH. SO NOW YOU WANNA DO IT
BY THE LAW OF THE CLAN?

13:01.737 --> 13:06.394
TRUST ME, CIRCLE BE HARSHER
THAN A HUNDRED OF ME.

13:06.524 --> 13:10.746
CUT YOUR FINGERS OFF, LIKE YOU
DID HASIL'S, ONE BY ONE.

13:10.877 --> 13:12.922
LET YOU STARVE IN HERE.

13:13.053 --> 13:17.927
OH, NO. A BULLET IN YOUR CHEST,
AND YOU BLEED TO DEATH SLOW.

13:18.058 --> 13:21.235
THAT'D BE MORE FITTIN'.
[ COCKS PISTOL ]

13:21.365 --> 13:22.802
[ GUNSHOT ]

13:22.932 --> 13:24.499
[ LAUGHS ]

13:24.629 --> 13:27.502
[ SIGHS ]
NO FARRELL EVER KILLED ANOTHER.

13:27.632 --> 13:30.244
I AIN'T GONNA BE THE ONE
TO CHANGE THAT.

13:30.374 --> 13:33.900
ONE OF THESE DAYS, SOMEBODY'S
GONNA END THAT TRADITION.

13:34.030 --> 13:38.339
I ONLY HOPE
THEY BE DOING IT TO YOU.

13:43.910 --> 13:45.389
[ PISTOL CLATTERS ]

13:49.959 --> 13:52.701
-YOU KNOW,
IF THIS KID'S A FARRELL,

13:52.832 --> 13:55.095
AND HE WAS DOWN HERE YESTERDAY,

13:55.225 --> 13:58.576
MEANS HE'S PROBABLY LINKED
TO THE ATTEMPTED ROBBERY, RIGHT?

13:58.707 --> 14:00.404
-IT'S POSSIBLE,
IFHE'S A FARRELL.

14:00.535 --> 14:03.712
BUT WE DON'T KNOW THAT.
-JESUS.

14:03.843 --> 14:06.193
[ SIGHS ]
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

14:06.323 --> 14:08.412
-HEY, YOU OKAY?

14:08.543 --> 14:10.850
-YEAH. I JUST HAVEN'T EATEN.

14:12.677 --> 14:15.115
-PROTEIN?

14:15.245 --> 14:17.944
-GOD, NO, MAN. PUT THAT AWAY.

14:18.074 --> 14:20.642
[ WRAPPER CRINKLES ]

14:20.772 --> 14:23.427
-ORGANIZE AN AUTOPSY
BEFORE WE DO ANYTHING.

14:23.558 --> 14:25.255
-ALL RIGHT.

14:37.833 --> 14:39.661
-HEY. HEY.
-I THINK I GOT ONE...

14:39.791 --> 14:42.533
-MISS? HEY.
HEY, I'M TALKING TO YOU. UH...

14:42.664 --> 14:43.883
-SHERIFF, HONESTLY, I NEED --
-LISTEN.

14:44.013 --> 14:45.319
I JUST NEED YOU
FOR SOMETHIN', OKAY?

14:45.449 --> 14:46.798
YOU'RE GONNA COME WITH ME.

14:46.929 --> 14:48.191
I AIN'T GONNA BUST YA,
ALL RIGHT?

14:48.322 --> 14:49.671
I JUST NEED YOU FOR SOMETHING.
OKAY?

14:49.801 --> 14:51.455
-W-W-WHY? WHY? WHERE WE GOIN'?

14:51.586 --> 14:52.892
-I'LL TELL YOU ON THE WAY.

14:53.022 --> 14:55.459
-ON THE WAY WHERE?! SH--

14:55.590 --> 14:58.158
[ DOOR RATTLES ]

15:00.769 --> 15:03.250
-I'M COUNTING ON YOU.
YOU KNOW THAT?

15:03.380 --> 15:05.992
-HOW'S NORWOOD?

15:06.122 --> 15:08.908
MY GRANDPA'S NAME WAS NORWOOD.

15:09.038 --> 15:10.822
-NORWOOD'S FINE.

15:10.953 --> 15:13.303
WHAT WAS HE WEARIN' AGAIN?

15:13.434 --> 15:14.914
-I GOT THIS.

15:18.526 --> 15:20.528
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

15:20.658 --> 15:22.617
-SAID HIS NAME WAS NORWOOD.

15:22.747 --> 15:24.793
KINDA LIKE
THIS HIPPIE KINDA KID

15:24.924 --> 15:27.970
OUT FROM BACK EAST --
YOU KNOW, RALEIGH COUNTY?

15:28.101 --> 15:31.104
HE -- HE HAD ON A GREEN...
GREEN SHIRT, I THINK.

15:31.234 --> 15:34.716
-WHAT KIND OF CAR HE HAVE?
-OH, HE -- WE WAS ON FOOT.

15:34.846 --> 15:36.152
-THEN WHERE'D YOU DO IT?

15:36.283 --> 15:37.980
-IN A PARKING LOT.

15:38.111 --> 15:40.113
UH, MORE LIKE A FILLING STATION,
YOU KNOW.

15:40.243 --> 15:42.332
UM, IT WAS OUT BY 60,
NEAR THE BORDER.

15:42.463 --> 15:46.423
IT WAS ALL COVERED IN CRABGRASS.
HE WAS REAL NICE.

15:46.554 --> 15:49.905
-THEN WHAT?
-WELL, THEN HE WAS WALKIN' AWAY,

15:50.036 --> 15:52.038
AND THESE THREE GUYS COME
IN A SHITTY WHITE VAN,

15:52.168 --> 15:53.735
AND THEY -- THEY KICKED HIS ASS

15:53.865 --> 15:55.041
AND THEN THEY THREW HIM
IN THE VAN

15:55.171 --> 15:56.956
AND THEN THEY -- THEY --
THEY DROVE OFF.

15:57.086 --> 15:59.349
-WHY'D YOU WAIT TO COME IN?

15:59.480 --> 16:01.525
-WELL, LIKE I'M CLAMORING
TO COME DOWN HERE

16:01.656 --> 16:05.181
AND TELL YOU GUYS ANYTHING.

16:05.312 --> 16:08.968
OH! AND HE HAD A -- HE HAD
A NECKLACE THINGADOODLE ON HIM.

16:09.098 --> 16:10.534
YOU KNOW, THAT HIS
OLD GIRLFRIEND MADE HIM?

16:10.665 --> 16:12.667
MADE OUT OF WEEDS OR SOMETHIN'.

16:12.797 --> 16:15.278
-ALL RIGHTY. THANK YOU, MA'AM.
-MM-HMM.

16:15.409 --> 16:17.454
[ TELEPHONE RINGING
IN DISTANCE ]

16:20.327 --> 16:23.634
-JUST GOT A CALL FROM
RALEIGH COUNTY, WEST VIRGINIA.

16:23.765 --> 16:26.594
STATE CLAIMED THE BODY.
SO, UH, WE CALLED THE E.M.S.

16:26.724 --> 16:29.162
THEY'RE GONNA TRANSPORT IT
UP TO CHARLESTON, UH, RIGHT NOW.

16:29.292 --> 16:34.994
-WELL, YOU HAVE 'EM CHECK
THE DMVs, UH, ON THE WHITE VAN.

16:35.124 --> 16:37.474
AND, UH, WE'LL SEE IF
ANYTHING POPS.

16:37.605 --> 16:39.259
OKAY.

16:39.389 --> 16:42.914
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS, FLIPS SHUT,
THUDS ]

16:43.045 --> 16:45.961
ROCK STAR OVER HERE. [ LAUGHS ]

16:46.092 --> 16:47.702
-SHUT UP.

16:47.832 --> 16:50.270
[ LAUGHS ]

16:50.400 --> 16:52.402
-ALL RIGHT, HERE WE ARE.
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]

16:52.533 --> 16:56.580
YOU GOT EVERYTHING?
-YEP. THANKS FOR THE RIDE.

16:56.711 --> 16:59.540
-HEY. UH, THANK YOU AGAIN.

16:59.670 --> 17:01.498
-YEP.

17:01.629 --> 17:04.458
-HEY, ONE MORE THING
I MIGHT ASK. UH...

17:04.588 --> 17:05.894
-YEAH?

17:07.939 --> 17:11.334
-UM, YOU...HAVE YOU GOT ANYTHING
ON YOU?

17:11.465 --> 17:13.902
-SERIOUSLY? [ SCOFFS ]

17:14.033 --> 17:17.253
-I MEAN, I GOT CASH.
I CAN PAY YOU.

17:17.384 --> 17:21.518
-I DON'T WANT ANYTHING ANYMORE
FROM YOU, SHERIFF.

17:21.649 --> 17:25.305
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?
YOU AND ME, WE ARE STRAIGHT.

17:25.435 --> 17:28.047
I GOT MY "GET OUT OF JAIL
FOR FREE" CARD ALREADY.

17:28.177 --> 17:31.354
AND FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,
ALL OF THIS? I DON'T CARE.

17:31.485 --> 17:33.574
YOU DO ONE MORE THING,
YOU COME NEAR ME ONE MORE TIME,

17:33.704 --> 17:35.837
AND I'LL GO TO THE STATE ON YOU.
DO YOU HEAR ME?

17:58.381 --> 17:59.948
[ ENGINE TURNS OFF ]

18:00.079 --> 18:01.471
[ TRUCK DOOR CLOSES ]

18:08.130 --> 18:09.436
-CAN I HELP YOU?

18:09.566 --> 18:11.568
-MY KIN WAS KILLED.

18:11.699 --> 18:14.223
I'M HERE TO CLAIM THE BODY.

18:16.965 --> 18:18.488
-[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

18:18.619 --> 18:21.187
I-I REMEMBER YOU.
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

18:21.317 --> 18:25.930
-ASA FARRELL.
-YEAH. WADE HOUGHTON.

18:26.061 --> 18:28.498
THAT WAS, UH, QUITE A SPEECH
YOU MADE AT THAT MEETING.

18:28.629 --> 18:30.109
-UH, YEAH, LOOK,

18:30.239 --> 18:32.459
I'M SORRY IF I CAUSED YOU
ANY TROUBLE, SHERIFF.

18:32.589 --> 18:34.983
-OH. UH...

18:35.114 --> 18:38.378
SO YOU SAY YOU HAD A, UH,
FAMILY MEMBER PASS ON?

18:38.508 --> 18:40.336
UM, YOU GOT A DESCRIPTION?

18:40.467 --> 18:42.904
-WELL, HOW MANY DEAD KIDS
YOU PICK UP TODAY?

18:43.034 --> 18:48.039
HE'S ABOUT 19, 20.
LONG BROWN HAIR. ONE OF US.

18:48.170 --> 18:51.042
-WELL, UH, WE DON'T GOT
NO UNIDENTIFIED BODIES

18:51.173 --> 18:53.001
ON PREMISES RIGHT NOW.

18:56.004 --> 18:57.701
-WELL, I WENT
TO THE HOSPITAL FIRST.

18:57.832 --> 18:59.225
THEY SAID HE WASN'T THERE,

18:59.355 --> 19:01.140
BUT EVERY DEAD BODY
HAS PAPERWORK, SHERIFF,

19:01.270 --> 19:03.098
AND THAT PAPERWORK'S
A MATTER OF PUBLIC RECORD,

19:03.229 --> 19:05.056
AND IT SAID
HE WAS IN THE MORGUE HERE.

19:05.187 --> 19:08.277
-MM. BOY. GODDAMN IT.

19:08.408 --> 19:10.018
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
YOU'RE, UH --

19:10.149 --> 19:12.238
WE -- YOU'RE RIGHT,
WE HAD A YOUNG MAN

19:12.368 --> 19:14.022
WHO WAS KILLED IN AN ACCIDENT
YESTERDAY.

19:14.153 --> 19:17.330
UM, MM,
BUT HIS BODY WAS CLAIMED.

19:17.460 --> 19:19.158
-CLAIMED BY WHO?

19:19.288 --> 19:22.465
-BY ANOTHER JURISDICTION.
BY RALEIGH COUNTY.

19:22.596 --> 19:24.728
-RALEIGH COUNTY, WEST VIRGINIA?
-THAT'S RIGHT.

19:24.859 --> 19:27.166
UH, THEY HAD
A MISSING PERSONS REPORT FILE.

19:27.296 --> 19:31.344
UM, IT MATCHED THE DESCRIPTION
OF THIS YOUNG MAN EXACTLY.

19:31.474 --> 19:33.607
AND WE SENT HIM OVER TO THEM,
SO...

19:33.737 --> 19:38.481
UH...IT CAN'T BE YOUR COUSIN.
I MEAN, I'M SORRY.

19:38.612 --> 19:42.181
-I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOUR GAME IS, SHERIFF,

19:42.311 --> 19:45.140
BUT THAT WASMY COUSIN TICE.

19:45.271 --> 19:48.230
AND HIS MOTHER, WHY,
SHE'S BESIDE HERSELF RIGHT NOW.

19:48.361 --> 19:49.884
I MEAN, LOSING SOMEONE'S HARD

19:50.014 --> 19:52.408
BECAUSE THEY'RE GONE
BUT THEY'RE STILL WITH YOU.

19:52.539 --> 19:55.759
I THINK YOU KNOW WHAT
I MEAN BY THAT, RIGHT?

19:55.890 --> 19:57.761
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

19:57.892 --> 20:01.417
-[ CHUCKLES ] UH, I HAVE
NO IDEA WHATSOEVER

20:01.548 --> 20:02.766
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

20:02.897 --> 20:05.291
-IF MY KIN ISN'T BURIED
ON OUR LAND,

20:05.421 --> 20:08.250
HIS SPIRIT WILL NOT REST.
YOU UNDERSTAND?

20:08.381 --> 20:10.557
-WELL, YOU KNOW, I MEAN,
I WAS RAISED A CHRISTIAN.

20:10.687 --> 20:13.603
-IF HIS SPIRIT DOESN'T REST,
WADE,

20:13.734 --> 20:17.128
IT'S GONNA COME FOR US.

20:17.259 --> 20:21.002
FOR HIS MOTHER. AND ME.

20:21.132 --> 20:23.091
AND THEN YOU, WADE.

20:24.397 --> 20:27.617
-HEY, UH,
WE GOT A STAFF MEETIN'.

20:27.748 --> 20:30.533
-I KNOW.
WELL, YOU TAKE CARE OF IT.

20:30.664 --> 20:32.187
-ALL RIGHT.

20:35.669 --> 20:37.627
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
-FOLLOW ME.

20:37.758 --> 20:40.195
-[ SIGHS ]

20:56.820 --> 21:00.781
-THE EDICT SAYS NO VISITORS,
BUT I-I DON'T CARE.

21:00.911 --> 21:04.263
BROUGHT YOU SOME CHICKEN,
POTATOES, CORN.

21:04.393 --> 21:07.266
-WHY WOULD I WANT ANYTHING
BRUNG BY YOU?

21:10.312 --> 21:12.445
-FA...

21:12.575 --> 21:15.230
I WAS ONLY GOING ALONG WITH IT
FOR SHOW.

21:15.361 --> 21:18.364
-WELL, FELT REAL TO ME.

21:18.494 --> 21:20.191
-[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

21:20.322 --> 21:22.672
IT ONLY WOULD'VE BEEN WORSE
IF I DIDN'T.

21:22.803 --> 21:24.979
-WORSE THAN THIS?

21:25.109 --> 21:27.895
I WOULD RATHER BE DEAD.

21:28.025 --> 21:30.027
MAYBE I AM DEAD.

21:30.158 --> 21:32.116
-NO.

21:32.247 --> 21:35.511
YOU'RE ALL WE GOT, FA.

21:35.642 --> 21:38.688
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE THAT KNOWS
WHAT WE SHOULD DO,

21:38.819 --> 21:42.126
KNOWS THE PRICE OF OUR LIVIN'.

21:42.257 --> 21:44.651
-YOU TELL SHURN

21:44.781 --> 21:46.566
THAT I PAIN FOR HER,

21:46.696 --> 21:49.220
AND I'M SORRY ABOUT HER TICE.

21:49.351 --> 21:50.526
-DID ALREADY.

21:52.354 --> 21:54.443
-MM.

21:54.574 --> 21:57.316
LOOK, I'M ONLY TRYING TO DO
WHAT'S RIGHT.

21:59.666 --> 22:01.232
AND WE GOT SET UP.

22:01.363 --> 22:04.018
-MAYBE THEM BOYS JUST WENT DOWN
TO THE SHOP TO...

22:04.148 --> 22:05.498
I DON'T KNOW, PLAY CARDS OR --

22:05.628 --> 22:08.022
-NO, I TOLD YOU.
IT WAS THEIR CHURCH DAY.

22:08.152 --> 22:10.851
NO, THEY WAS WAITIN'.

22:10.981 --> 22:12.592
THEY KNEW WE WAS COMIN'.

22:12.722 --> 22:14.855
-I GO TALK TO THE ELDERS,
GET A CIRCLE CALLED.

22:14.985 --> 22:16.596
THEY'LL UNDERSTAND WHY
YOU DEFIED THE BREN'IN

22:16.726 --> 22:18.162
AND HOW IT ALL WENT DARK

22:18.293 --> 22:19.947
'CAUSE THERE WAS SOME KIND
OF FORCES AT WORK --

22:20.077 --> 22:24.647
-NO, AIN'T NO POINT IN THAT.
AND THERE WEREN'T NO FORCES.

22:24.778 --> 22:28.390
NO, IT WAS ONE OF US
WHO BETRAYED ME.

22:28.521 --> 22:31.741
ONE OF OUR OWN WHO HAS
OTHER IDEAS ABOUT THINGS.

22:31.872 --> 22:33.395
-NO, I NEVER TOLD G'WINVEER.

22:35.658 --> 22:37.356
-DID I SAY YOU DID?

22:39.662 --> 22:42.665
[ CHAINS RATTLING ]
[ GRUNTS ]

22:42.796 --> 22:45.712
LOOK.

22:45.842 --> 22:49.542
I'VE BEEN DOIN'
A LOT OF THINKIN',

22:49.672 --> 22:51.195
SO I KNOW WHAT WE GOTTA DO

22:51.326 --> 22:54.024
TO SOLVE THIS
AND EVERY OTHER PROBLEM WE GOT.

22:54.155 --> 22:55.504
-YEAH. WHAT IS IT, FA?

22:55.635 --> 22:57.419
-[ SIGHS HEAVILY ]

22:57.550 --> 22:59.334
NOW, YOU...

22:59.465 --> 23:03.294
YOU CARE ABOUT THIS FAMILY MORE
THAN ANYONE ON THIS MOUNTAIN.

23:03.425 --> 23:05.427
-YEAH.
-RIGHT? AND I CHERISH THAT.

23:05.558 --> 23:07.647
I NEED YOU TO DO SOMETHING
FOR ME.

23:09.475 --> 23:10.954
I GOT NO ONE ELSE TO GO TO.

23:11.085 --> 23:13.348
-I-I CAN'T HELP YOU, FA.

23:13.479 --> 23:15.785
-I JUST NEED ONE THING.

23:20.877 --> 23:23.445
-HOW MANY OF Y'ALL ARE UP THERE?

23:23.576 --> 23:25.447
60?

23:25.578 --> 23:27.362
[ THUNDERCLAP ]

23:27.493 --> 23:29.103
MORE?

23:29.233 --> 23:31.497
-IT'S NOT THE NUMBER
THAT MATTERS.

23:31.627 --> 23:32.846
-WHAT MATTERS?

23:32.976 --> 23:34.413
-WHAT WE BELIEVE IN.

23:34.543 --> 23:36.632
-WHICH IS?

23:36.763 --> 23:39.026
-OUR FREEDOM.

23:40.375 --> 23:42.029
-ARE YOU THE LEADER?

23:42.159 --> 23:45.206
-[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ] NO.

23:46.642 --> 23:49.558
-SO HOW'S IT WORK?
YOU GOT, LIKE, A CHIEF?

23:49.689 --> 23:52.082
A...A KING?

23:52.213 --> 23:54.345
-[ LAUGHS ]

23:54.476 --> 23:57.348
WHAT IS THAT? WHY DO YOU ASSUME
IT WOULD BE A GUY?

23:57.479 --> 23:59.263
HMM?

23:59.394 --> 24:01.570
-YOU GOT A QUEEN.

24:01.701 --> 24:03.616
-NOT EXACTLY.
[ THUNDERCLAP ]

24:03.746 --> 24:05.444
-HEY, I'M JUST -- I'M ASKING

24:05.574 --> 24:09.056
'CAUSE I NEVER HAD ANY
INTERACTION WITH Y'ALL BEFORE.

24:09.186 --> 24:11.362
-SEEMS LIKE YOU HAVEN'T HAD
MUCH REAL INTERACTION

24:11.493 --> 24:12.973
WITH ANYBODY LATELY.

24:13.103 --> 24:15.105
I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND ME
SAYING THAT.

24:15.236 --> 24:18.544
-NO, I MEAN,
YOU CAN SAY WHAT YOU LIKE.

24:18.674 --> 24:21.024
YOU WANT ME TO BE HONEST?
I'LL SAY THIS --

24:21.155 --> 24:23.418
YOU'RE NOT JUST DOWN HERE
'CAUSE THAT BOY'S YOUR KIN.

24:23.549 --> 24:26.029
[ THUNDERCLAP ]

24:26.160 --> 24:28.075
NO, THERE'S SOME OTHER REASON.

24:28.205 --> 24:31.339
[ THUNDERCLAP ]
-SUCH AS?

24:31.470 --> 24:33.863
-I DON'T READILY KNOW.

24:33.994 --> 24:36.431
I'LL PUT SOME MUSIC ON.
[ RADIO TURNS ON ]

24:36.562 --> 24:39.869
[ POP MUSIC PLAYING ]

24:40.000 --> 24:44.178
♪♪

24:44.308 --> 24:46.310
-THAT'S NOT MUSIC.

24:46.441 --> 24:47.877
♪♪

24:48.008 --> 24:51.490
-YEAH.
YEAH, I BELIEVE YOU'RE RIGHT.

24:51.620 --> 24:53.796
[ KNOB CLICKS, RADIO TURNS OFF ]

24:53.927 --> 24:55.276
[ SIGHS ]

24:55.406 --> 24:57.539
[ METAL CLANKING ]

24:57.670 --> 24:59.759
[ SCRAPING SOUND ]

24:59.889 --> 25:04.328
-HOW'S YOUR FA DOIN'?

25:04.459 --> 25:05.939
-HE'S OKAY, I GUESS.

25:06.069 --> 25:08.594
SAID HE'S HAD SOME TIME
TO THINK.

25:08.724 --> 25:10.378
BROUGHT HIM SOME CHICKEN,
THEN...

25:10.509 --> 25:11.945
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

25:12.075 --> 25:13.990
WENT OVER TO MORNINGSIDE
FOR A WALK

25:14.121 --> 25:15.949
AND HAD ME A THINK, TOO.

25:16.079 --> 25:18.342
-HEY, WILL YOU GIVE ME A HAND
WITH THIS?

25:21.868 --> 25:26.002
-THAT BOY TICE --
YOU KNOW HIM MUCH?

25:26.133 --> 25:28.527
-NOT THAT MUCH.

25:28.657 --> 25:30.964
-YEAH. HIS MAMA KNEW HIM.

25:31.094 --> 25:33.444
KNEW HIM ALL HIS LIFE.

25:33.575 --> 25:35.664
-YEAH.

25:35.795 --> 25:37.536
POOR SHURN.

25:39.842 --> 25:43.629
-LIKE I SAID,
I DID SOME THINKIN'.

25:43.759 --> 25:46.109
I THINK WE WERE SET UP
AT THAT SHOP.

25:46.240 --> 25:48.895
[ CLANK ]
SET UP AND KNOCKED DOWN.

25:49.025 --> 25:51.898
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

25:52.028 --> 25:53.987
THEY KNEW WE WAS COMING.

25:55.554 --> 25:58.295
STRANGE, ISN'T IT, G'WIN?

26:00.167 --> 26:01.995
-STRANGE LIKE YOU NOT TELLING ME

26:02.125 --> 26:04.693
WHAT YOU WERE REALLY UP TO
THAT DAY?

26:04.824 --> 26:07.304
-THAT'S WHY YOU WAS HOLDING ON
TO THAT GOOD LUCK SHELL?

26:07.435 --> 26:08.915
YOU MUST'VE BEEN HOLDING IT
THE WHOLE TIME.

26:09.045 --> 26:10.525
-I KNEW YOU WERE UP TO NO GOOD,

26:10.656 --> 26:12.005
AND I DIDN'T WANT YOU
TO GET HURT.

26:12.135 --> 26:14.355
-WELL, THEN YOU GOT LUCKY
ON ACCOUNT OF ME.

26:14.485 --> 26:16.487
POOR OLD TICE? NOT SO MUCH.

26:16.618 --> 26:18.577
DON'T YOU FEEL YOU SHOULD GO
TALK TO HIS MOMMY?

26:18.707 --> 26:20.840
YOU GOT A DUTY TO HER NOW?
-DO I?

26:26.541 --> 26:28.021
FOSTER, ALL I WAS JUST --

26:28.151 --> 26:29.544
-[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]
IT'S DONE WITH.

26:29.675 --> 26:31.590
IT STAYS BETWEEN YOU AND ME.

26:31.720 --> 26:35.158
[ THUNDERCLAP ]

26:35.289 --> 26:37.770
[ ZIPPER WHIRS ]

26:37.900 --> 26:39.815
[ EQUIPMENT BEEPING ]

26:44.907 --> 26:48.258
-NOT SURE I SAW AN AMBO
OR A BLACK-AND-WHITE OUT THERE.

26:48.389 --> 26:51.522
-UH, NO, MA'AM,
I BROUGHT MY OWN TRUCK.

26:51.653 --> 26:54.482
-NOT SURE WE CAN AUTHORIZE
A PRIVATE VEHICLE FOR TRANSPORT.

26:54.613 --> 26:57.354
-WELL, WE DO THINGS
DIFFERENT ACROSS THE BORDER.

26:57.485 --> 26:59.661
-YOU SURE AS HELL DO.

27:07.887 --> 27:10.150
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

27:16.983 --> 27:18.985
-EVENING, FOSTER.

27:20.813 --> 27:22.684
HOW YOU DOIN' TONIGHT?

27:22.815 --> 27:24.207
-HOW YOU THINK, BOY?

27:24.338 --> 27:26.949
[ CHAINS RATTLING ]

27:27.080 --> 27:29.299
-I JUST WANTED TO COME ON DOWN
HERE AND SAY SORRY

27:29.430 --> 27:31.911
FOR DELIVERING THE SAD NEWS
THAT GOT YOU LOCKED UP.

27:32.041 --> 27:34.565
BUT...

27:34.696 --> 27:36.655
THAT'S THE WAY IT WAS.

27:36.785 --> 27:38.961
LADY RAY WAS ASKIN'.

27:39.092 --> 27:40.615
-[ CLEARS THROAT ]

27:40.746 --> 27:43.618
I GOT NO QUARREL WITH YOU
ON THAT COUNT.

27:43.749 --> 27:46.534
-MM, YEAH, NOT FROM WHERE
YOU STAND, YOU DON'T.

27:48.579 --> 27:52.496
SAY, I GOT ME SOME WINE
FROM KRAKE'S PRIVATE STOCK.

27:52.627 --> 27:54.063
YOU WANT SOME?

27:54.194 --> 27:55.978
-NO, THANK YOU.

27:56.109 --> 27:57.850
-YOU SURE?
-NO.

27:57.980 --> 28:01.897
-I CAN UNDERSTAND WHY MAYBE
YOU WOULDN'T WANT TO PARTAKE

28:02.028 --> 28:04.117
IN THIS PARTICULAR BATCH.

28:04.247 --> 28:06.685
BUT I REALLY THINK YOU SHOULD

28:06.815 --> 28:09.731
BECAUSE IT'S JUST --
IT'S JUST A FINE BREW.

28:09.862 --> 28:12.952
[ SNIFFS ] MMM.

28:13.082 --> 28:15.911
IT'S HANDMADE, YOU MIGHT SAY.

28:19.523 --> 28:21.874
[ SPLASHES ]
-UGH!

28:22.004 --> 28:24.050
[ JAR CLATTERS ]

28:24.180 --> 28:28.271
YOU ARE GONNA PAY
FOR THIS DISRESPECT, BOY.

28:29.795 --> 28:32.058
-I ALREADY PAID.

28:35.496 --> 28:37.498
[ BOTTLE RATTLING ]

28:37.628 --> 28:40.457
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

28:40.588 --> 28:43.417
-OH, WHAT'S THE MATTER?
YOU SCARED?

28:43.547 --> 28:44.679
HUH?

28:44.810 --> 28:46.115
YOU SCARED TO DIE?

28:46.246 --> 28:48.901
-BULLSHIT.
-BULLSHIT.

28:49.031 --> 28:50.641
-GO AHEAD! LIGHT ME UP!

28:52.818 --> 28:55.734
-CALM DOWN.
I AIN'T GONNA LIGHT YOU UP.

28:58.171 --> 29:01.043
REALLY, I JUST WANTED
TO SEE THIS. [ GASPS ]

29:02.784 --> 29:05.874
YOU AND ME, WE EVEN NOW.

29:06.005 --> 29:08.050
THAT'S IT.

29:26.939 --> 29:28.854
-MAN, I CAN NEVER GET USED
TO SEEING

29:28.984 --> 29:31.378
A YOUNG KID GET KILLED
LIKE THAT.

29:31.508 --> 29:34.033
-KILLED BY WHO?

29:34.163 --> 29:36.035
-WHO KNOWS? THERE WAS
AN EYEWITNESS CAME FORWARD,

29:36.165 --> 29:39.081
SAID THEY SAW HIM GETTING THROWN
INTO THE BACK OF A VAN.

29:39.212 --> 29:40.866
HE WAS GETTING BEAT UP.

29:40.996 --> 29:42.476
IT'S GOTTA BE DRUGS.

29:42.606 --> 29:44.304
-WELL, HE'D NEVER BEEN
OFF THE MOUNTAIN BEFORE,

29:44.434 --> 29:46.262
SO I KINDA DOUBT IT.

29:46.393 --> 29:48.874
-SOMEONE SURE TOOK ISSUE
WITH HIM.

29:49.004 --> 29:50.614
-WHO?

29:50.745 --> 29:53.400
-I KNOW AS MUCH AS YOU DO.

29:53.530 --> 29:56.925
-I SAW THE M.E. REPORT
IN YOUR HANDS THERE.

29:57.056 --> 29:59.972
IT SAID 10-47
BASED ON HIS INJURIES.

30:00.102 --> 30:01.887
THAT'S A HIT-AND-RUN.

30:02.017 --> 30:05.238
I MEAN, HE HAD WINDSHIELD GLASS
EMBEDDED IN HIS SCALP, RIGHT?

30:05.368 --> 30:08.981
-I CAN TELL YOU, WE WILL
BE DOIN' A FULL INVESTIGATION.

30:09.111 --> 30:11.810
-WELL, HOW THE HELL DID HE END
UP IN WEST VIRGINIA, ANYWAY?

30:11.940 --> 30:13.855
-HOW WOULD I KNOW THAT?

30:13.986 --> 30:15.901
-YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

30:16.031 --> 30:20.601
YOU LIVE FOR A WHILE
WITHOUT TV AND VIDEO GAMES

30:20.731 --> 30:22.037
AND ALL THESE DISTRACTIONS,

30:22.168 --> 30:24.823
YOU'RE NOT NUMBED OUT
ALL THE TIME.

30:24.953 --> 30:28.304
YOU LEARN HOW TO LISTEN TO
THE QUALITY OF A PERSON'S VOICE,

30:28.435 --> 30:30.002
READ THEIR FACE.

30:32.134 --> 30:34.310
WHAT I'M TRYING TO SAY IS, WADE,

30:34.441 --> 30:37.792
I KNOW YOU'RE LYING TO ME.

30:43.842 --> 30:46.279
-MY DADDY...

30:46.409 --> 30:48.368
YOU KNOW, HE WORKED
FOR THE COAL COMPANY.

30:48.498 --> 30:53.286
NOT THIS ONE. IT WAS ANOTHER ONE
THAT WAS CALLED, UM, BILOXI.

30:53.416 --> 30:56.767
WHEN I WAS A LITTLE BOY,
THEY SENT HIM UP THE MOUNTAIN,

30:56.898 --> 30:59.118
THROW YOU FOLKS OFF OF THERE.

30:59.248 --> 31:00.771
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

31:00.902 --> 31:02.904
DID NOT END WELL.

31:03.035 --> 31:05.515
TWO DAYS LATER,

31:05.646 --> 31:07.866
HE WAS STRUCK
AND KILLED BY LIGHTNING.

31:07.996 --> 31:09.389
ONE MONTH LATER WAS

31:09.519 --> 31:11.870
THE GREAT LOWER FORK MINE
EXPLOSION.

31:12.000 --> 31:14.220
11 MEN DIED THAT DAY
UNDER THE GROUND.

31:14.350 --> 31:16.787
AND I SAID TO MYSELF,
"I WILL NOT GO TO WORK FOR THEM.

31:16.918 --> 31:19.225
"I WILL NOT GO TO WORK
FOR BIG COAL.

31:19.355 --> 31:20.835
I'M GONNA HELP PEOPLE."

31:20.966 --> 31:22.881
I WENT INTO LAW ENFORCEMENT,

31:23.011 --> 31:26.710
AND HERE I AM, TASKED WITH
THE JOB OF EVICTING YOU.

31:26.841 --> 31:28.538
AND THAT IS NOT THE SIDE
THAT I WANNA BE ON.

31:28.669 --> 31:30.584
YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

31:30.714 --> 31:32.847
-WHOSE SIDE ARE YOU ON, WADE?

31:32.978 --> 31:35.458
-WHO DO YOU GODDAMN THINK?

31:35.589 --> 31:37.504
THAT'S WHY I'M DOING THIS.

31:37.634 --> 31:40.986
I WANT YOU TO KNOW,
I MEAN YOU FOLKS NO HARM.

31:45.033 --> 31:47.035
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

31:51.431 --> 31:53.128
[ ENGINE IDLING ]

31:53.259 --> 31:56.131
[ THUD ]
[ GASPS ]

32:00.657 --> 32:03.660
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]
-MAYBE I SHOULD DRIVE.

32:03.791 --> 32:05.097
-YEAH.

32:05.227 --> 32:06.620
[ SEAT BELT CLICKS ]

32:11.712 --> 32:14.715
[ WHIRRING ]

32:14.845 --> 32:16.021
-ELDERBERRY?

32:16.151 --> 32:17.631
-DEWBERRY.

32:17.761 --> 32:19.546
-OF COURSE.

32:19.676 --> 32:23.028
BUT IT'S NOT DOING LIKE IT WAS.

32:23.158 --> 32:26.118
[ CHUCKLES ]
AH...

32:26.248 --> 32:28.555
I GET MORE TIRED EVERY DAY.
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

32:28.685 --> 32:30.078
-YOU LIKE A BATH?

32:31.471 --> 32:33.386
I'LL GET THE BOYS
TO BRING SOME WATER UP.

32:33.516 --> 32:36.519
-NOW THAT'S A FINE THOUGHT.
THANK YOU.

32:36.650 --> 32:38.391
-I'LL GO AND FETCH 'EM.

32:39.783 --> 32:42.961
-I WANTED TO ASK YOU,
DID YOU GET AN ANSWER?

32:44.353 --> 32:45.659
-TO WHAT?

32:45.789 --> 32:47.269
-TO THIS --

32:47.400 --> 32:49.184
CAN YOU TRUST HIM?

32:49.315 --> 32:51.186
AND YOU KNOW WHO I MEAN.

32:53.972 --> 32:56.887
-WELL, HE'S DOWN THERE
GETTIN' THE BOY'S BODY.

32:57.018 --> 33:00.413
-HE'S A BRAVE SOUL, HE IS.

33:00.543 --> 33:04.025
BUT EVERY TIME
I LOOK AT THAT ASA,

33:04.156 --> 33:06.288
IT'S LIKE I'M SEEIN' DOUBLE.

33:06.419 --> 33:10.684
TWO PEOPLE.
ONE DARK, THE OTHER GOOD.

33:12.077 --> 33:15.863
PROPHECY TALK
OF ONE WHO RETURNS.

33:15.994 --> 33:20.999
I THOUGHT ALL ALONG
THAT HE WAS THAT ONE.

33:21.129 --> 33:25.612
BUT NOW I'M NOT SURE
IF IT'S HIM SHOULD LEAD US.

33:32.358 --> 33:34.186
-WHY NOT?

33:34.316 --> 33:36.710
-THE STRONGEST SHOULD.

33:36.840 --> 33:40.322
AND YOU DO AGREETH WITH ME
ON THAT?

33:40.453 --> 33:42.933
-W-WELL, YES, MA'AM, BUT...

33:43.064 --> 33:44.370
WHO IS THAT?

33:44.500 --> 33:46.372
-YOU KNOW WHO IT IS...

33:47.677 --> 33:49.984
AND SO DO I.

33:50.115 --> 33:52.465
-OH, MA'AM, I...

33:52.595 --> 33:54.293
I DON'T KNOW WHAT EXACTLY --

33:54.423 --> 33:58.036
-OH, DON'T PLAY HUMBLE NOW,
GIRL.

33:58.166 --> 34:02.040
YOU KNOW YOUR POWER
AND YOU KNOW WHAT YOU WANT.

34:02.170 --> 34:05.043
DON'T BE AFRAID OF IT.

34:08.785 --> 34:10.091
-YES, MA'AM.

34:13.616 --> 34:17.229
-YOU ARE A TRUE DAUGHTER
OF THIS MOUNTAIN.

34:19.274 --> 34:23.800
YOU ARE ITS BLOOD AND ITS FIRE.

34:35.812 --> 34:38.728
[ INSECTS CHIRPING,
ANIMAL HOWLS IN DISTANCE ]

34:43.864 --> 34:46.519
-FOSTER. YOU AWAKE?

34:46.649 --> 34:48.564
-[ GROANS ]

34:48.695 --> 34:49.826
-NEED ANYTHING?

34:49.957 --> 34:53.091
-NO.

34:53.221 --> 34:57.051
-BROUGHT YOU SOME SMOKES.
I KNOW YOU LIKE 'EM.

34:58.922 --> 35:02.404
YOUR BOY WAS JUST TRYING
TO MAKE THINGS EASIER.

35:02.535 --> 35:06.626
WE'LL GET YA OUT OF HERE.
DON'T WORRY.

35:06.756 --> 35:08.149
-[ MUMBLES ]

35:18.203 --> 35:21.119
[ DOOR CREAKING ]

35:24.644 --> 35:26.646
-HOW'D YOU DO IT?

35:26.776 --> 35:28.430
HOW'D YOU GET OUT?

35:30.084 --> 35:32.130
-I AIN'T GONNA BE LONG.

35:36.482 --> 35:39.093
LOOK AT YOU.

35:40.747 --> 35:43.402
I AIN'T NEVER SEEN YOU NAKED
LIKE THIS BEFORE.

35:43.532 --> 35:46.100
-SURE YOU DID,
ONLY YOU DON'T REMEMBER.

35:46.231 --> 35:49.277
YOU WERE JUST A BABY,

35:49.408 --> 35:53.890
SWEET LITTLE THING I COULD HOLD
IN ONE HAND LIKE A DOLL.

35:54.021 --> 35:57.198
-IN ONE HAND LIKE A DOLL

35:57.329 --> 35:59.896
SO'S YOU COULD BEAT ME
WITH THE OTHER.

36:02.247 --> 36:06.251
YOU WERE RIGHT, WHAT YOU SAID.

36:06.381 --> 36:10.342
ONE OF US IS BOUND TO BREAK
THE RULE.

36:10.472 --> 36:14.302
A FARRELL'S GONNA KILL ANOTHER
ONE OF THESE DAYS,

36:14.433 --> 36:17.392
ONLY THAT DAY,

36:17.523 --> 36:20.526
IT'S NOW.
[ COCKS PISTOL ]

36:20.656 --> 36:22.267
-I SEEN IT COMING.

36:23.746 --> 36:27.881
PROPHECY SAY A DEMON AMONG US,

36:28.011 --> 36:30.318
AND I KNOW WHO IT BE.

36:33.713 --> 36:36.803
PROMISE ME JUST ONE THING,
CHILD.

36:36.933 --> 36:39.153
DON'T LEAVE ME HERE.

36:39.284 --> 36:44.767
TAKE ME TO THE BED
SO'S I WON'T BE FOUND LIKE THIS.

36:44.898 --> 36:47.248
-YEAH, MA.

36:47.379 --> 36:48.902
I WILL.

36:50.643 --> 36:53.733
BUT YOU DIDN'T SEE THIS COMING,

36:53.863 --> 36:56.562
'CAUSE YOU AIN'T SEEN NOTHING
COMING.

36:56.692 --> 36:58.694
AND THAT'S WHY I'M DOING THIS.

36:58.825 --> 37:02.829
THIS FAMILY NEEDS A LEADER
WHO SEES, WHO'S READY TO FIGHT.

37:02.959 --> 37:05.092
-YOU THINK I GOT NO FIGHT?

37:05.223 --> 37:09.792
-NO, I THINK THAT YOU ARE
TWISTED IN THE HEAD,

37:09.923 --> 37:15.363
IMAGINING OLD WAYS AND TALES
EVEN A CHILD KNOWS IS FOOLERY.

37:15.494 --> 37:17.931
-IS THEY?

37:18.061 --> 37:19.889
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW?

37:20.020 --> 37:23.284
-'CAUSE IF ANY OF IT WAS TRUE,

37:23.415 --> 37:27.288
I WOULDN'T BE HERE,
DOING WHAT I'M ABOUT TO DO.

37:27.419 --> 37:30.378
-HOW DO YOU EVEN KNOW
YOU CAN DO IT?

37:32.206 --> 37:34.861
YOU AIN'T EVEN TRIED YET.

37:34.991 --> 37:37.429
-[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

37:50.833 --> 37:55.098
[ BREATHES SHARPLY ]

37:59.755 --> 38:03.193
[ WATER GURGLING ]

38:03.324 --> 38:05.674
[ BREATHES SHARPLY ]

38:07.502 --> 38:10.113
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

38:13.552 --> 38:15.728
[ RAGGED BREATHING ]

38:15.858 --> 38:18.905
[ WATER GURGLING ]

38:19.035 --> 38:21.995
[ RAGGED BREATHING CONTINUES ]

38:24.171 --> 38:26.521
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

38:32.745 --> 38:34.007
[ SETS DOWN PISTOL ]

38:36.444 --> 38:40.492
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

38:54.680 --> 38:56.116
-WHY ARE WE STOPPING HERE?

38:56.246 --> 38:58.771
[ TURNS OFF ENGINE ]

38:58.901 --> 39:00.468
[ TRUCK DOOR CLOSES ]

39:11.436 --> 39:13.351
-COME ON, GIVE ME A HAND.

39:25.972 --> 39:27.669
STRANGE.

39:27.800 --> 39:30.498
-WHAT'S THAT?

39:30.629 --> 39:32.631
-YOU CAN'T EVEN LOOK AT HIM.

39:35.111 --> 39:37.287
YOU'VE SEEN DEAD BODIES.

39:37.418 --> 39:39.725
YOU'VE BEEN A COP FOR A WHILE.

39:43.293 --> 39:45.121
-IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

39:48.255 --> 39:49.822
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

39:49.952 --> 39:52.041
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

39:52.172 --> 39:54.000
HE COME OUT OF NOWHERE.

39:54.130 --> 39:56.872
I WAS TURNING AROUND,
HE WAS THERE.

39:57.003 --> 39:59.092
YOU GOTTA TELL YOUR PEOPLE
I'M SORRY.

39:59.222 --> 40:02.008
I DIDN'T MEAN TO HURT HIM.
YOU CAN'T...

40:02.138 --> 40:04.227
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

40:04.358 --> 40:05.751
I HAVE A LITTLE BOY.

40:05.881 --> 40:07.013
UHH!

40:07.143 --> 40:09.276
-YOU LISTEN TO ME, WADE.

40:09.407 --> 40:10.843
THAT MOUNTAIN'S GONNA
COME FOR YOU.

40:10.973 --> 40:13.628
YOU UNDERSTAND ME?
JUST LIKE IT DID YOUR DADDY.

40:13.759 --> 40:15.282
NOW YOU'RE GONNA MAKE 'EM STOP.

40:15.413 --> 40:17.371
YOU'RE GONNA MAKE 'EM
BACK OFF FOR GOOD.

40:17.502 --> 40:19.460
OR YOUR LITTLE BOY --

40:19.591 --> 40:21.549
HE'S DEAD.

40:21.680 --> 40:23.421
[ THUD ]

40:25.510 --> 40:28.382
-[ PANTING ]

40:28.513 --> 40:31.124
[ STARTS ENGINE ]
-LEAVE US ALONE, WADE.

40:37.826 --> 40:40.220
[ PANTING ]

40:40.350 --> 40:43.005
[ ENGINE RUMBLING ]

40:53.799 --> 40:56.410
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

40:56.541 --> 40:58.325
[ ENGINE TURNS OFF ]

41:10.511 --> 41:11.991
-[ GASPS ]

41:12.121 --> 41:14.254
[ GASPING ]

41:14.384 --> 41:15.864
[ Voice breaks ] THANK YOU.

41:15.995 --> 41:18.650
[ CRYING ]

41:18.780 --> 41:20.478
[ CRIES ] THANK YOU, ASA.

41:20.608 --> 41:23.481
[ PEOPLE MURMURING ]

41:23.611 --> 41:26.571
[ CRYING ]

41:26.701 --> 41:29.399
-WHAT'S GOING ON?

42:07.394 --> 42:10.789
-THE BREN'IN IS DEAD.

42:10.919 --> 42:13.487
LONG LIVE THE BREN'IN.

42:13.618 --> 42:16.534
[ SELUAH'S "NANON" PLAYING ]

42:23.802 --> 42:29.111
-♪ PRAISE THE LORD

42:29.242 --> 42:33.942
♪ SHE'S IN MY ARMS AGAIN

42:40.732 --> 42:44.823
♪ PRAISE THE LORD

42:47.652 --> 42:50.263
-FOSTER...

42:50.393 --> 42:51.786
A DREADFUL DAY.

42:54.528 --> 42:57.313
YOUR MOTHER HAS PASSED.

42:58.663 --> 43:02.362
-♪ PRAISE THE LORD

43:04.669 --> 43:09.412
♪ SHE'S IN MY ARMS AGAIN

43:13.112 --> 43:15.897
-THEN KNEEL BEFORE YOUR KING.
